title: About
text: Hi! I’m Pranav Chivukula, a rising senior at Lexington High School. Right now, I’m learning how to make Quarto Websites on RStudio! You can also find me listening to music (BIG Mac Miller fan), playing Ultimate Frisbee, or hanging with friends.

About the Project
This project is called Fuel Efficiency and Weight. It analyzes how increasing the weight of the car affects the miles per gallon of said car.
